page 107 exercise #11

prompt user for name hours worked, rate of pay
calculate net pay,
display name, hours, rate, net pay

String iName, oNetPay
Int iHours
Double iRate, cNetPay

Main
	display "Enter Name: "
	get iName
	display "Enter Hours: "
	get iHours
	display "Enter Pay Rate: "
	get iRate
	
	cNetPay = iHours * iRate
	
	String oHours = format(iHours)
	String oRate = format(iRate)
	String oNetPay = format(iNetPay)
	
	Display "Wage information for " + iName + ": "
	Display "Hours: " +oHours
	Display "Rate: " + oRate
	Display "Net Pay: " + oNetPay
end-main
	
